{"tid":12847,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"年尾先黎裁員………花紅都慳返！正！","createTime":"2016-11-29T23:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2016-11-30T00:58:47.000Z","uid":29314,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d55028cc2c18caaf743666deadc9be0368cee375","tid":12847,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:10:30.000Z","msg":"根據傳媒日前報道，渣打銀行（02888）&hellip;調整&hellip;企業及機構銀行部門，料會有數十名員工受到影響，裁員行動本周開始。<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n普遍金融界裁員的時間表，都會選擇在年尾或年頭發生，點解？<br />\n<br />\n&hellip;&hellip;嘗試去綜合業界意見，可能會得出兩大結論：<br />\n<br />\n一是節省花紅；<br />\n<br />\n二是很多金融企業都會在年尾紛紛進行各式各樣的evaluation及所謂來年大計brainstorming offsite meeting，而很多高層主管都會在這些時候紛紛「獻計」，於是形成了一個現象，就是年尾年頭&hellip;&hellip;成為了裁員高峰期。"},{"pid":"3ffebd143b2e7ab254b994ea167b8d189d1f941b","tid":12847,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:15:12.000Z","msg":"最垃圾公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"535df07960fbb485ded6e4cdbdc501417d83fe69","tid":12847,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:25:30.000Z","msg":"近幾年好多公司都係咁"},{"pid":"a6385a78b38622c4fb9bbcaf8f02313f4e4a6a96","tid":12847,"uid":37661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:29:26.000Z","msg":"慳番個花紅做代通知金都係一條數，大把公司係咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"790c98dd39fe080f563840d266db615e9831bd0d","tid":12847,"uid":20943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:30:40.000Z","msg":"屌仲大條道理咁架wo<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c6e4ba0a355455d3a0b123aae4060907e6a0b0a","tid":12847,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-11-29T23:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>慳番個花紅做代通知金都係一條數，大把公司係咁。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji